seo.description: Contribute to the protocol by developing on the open source code

hero.title: Protocol Development
paragraphs: The YOUR Protocol is an open source protocol that allows developers to participate in code development and receive rewards for their contributions.
The protocol is designed to be developed by its community for its community, and provides developers with the tools and resources to improve the ecosystem.

intro.title: Contribute to the open source YOUR protocol and Earn

block1.title: Open source protocol
paragraphs: The YOUR Protocol is designed to be open source, meaning that anyone can contribute to the development of the protocol.

This allows developers from all over the world to collaborate on projects, share ideas and improve the protocol. By providing rewards for their contributions, it encourages developers to continue contributing to the protocol and encourages innovation.

block2.title: Develop the future together
paragraphs: Sign up and become part of the developer community of YOUR
Start contributing today to bring the protocol to the next level and earn
